title: [Jineve's Cookery, Backyard]
description: Surrounded on all sides by tufts of wide-bladed beach grass, the backyard's center is filled with fine grains of white sand that glisten in the sunlight.  Burning merrily in the center is a crackling fire that is built within a small pit and ringed by blackened stones.  An open archway leads into a small stucco-faced store.
